    <data name="ModuleHelp.Text">
        <value>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;h3&gt;Managing Subscriptions&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;There are two areas where you can control subscriptions&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ol&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Manage Subscriptions in the module itself&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;The Scheduler in the Host Menu&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ol&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;By default the scheduler is setup to send out e-mail notifications every hour. That means that once per hour the module will check if unsent notifications are due and sends them. If you wish to change this behaviour, you need to be logged on as host.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ol&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Log on with a host account&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Go to Host &amp;gt; Schedule&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Click on the &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;pencil symbol&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt; next to &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;
            pnc.Publisher.MagicNews.NewsNotification&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Set the &lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;Time Lapse / Retry frequency&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; values to your 
            preferred settings&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Leave anything else as is&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Make sure that &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Schedule Enebled&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt; is checked&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Click on &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Update&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Also make sure that the scheduler mode in Host Settings is set to &lt;i&gt;Timer Method&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ol&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;To manage your current subscriptions go to the&lt;i&gt; Magic News &lt;/i&gt;module that 
        you wish to manage and select &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Manage Subscriptions &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;from the Action 
        Menu.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ol&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Select the language&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt; that you would like to manage 
            subscriptions for&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Delete subscriptions by clicking on &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Delete&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt; next to each 
            subscriptin&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
